column5: to the spring fishing show to the first person who can tell me the answer to these two questions:   #1 When is Dave Mercer giving his seminar at the spring fishing show on Saturday.  AND  #2 Can you name the phobia that means a fear of fish?  Please answer if you can attend!!!
Looks Like bigugli's got them... pm me your full contact info!!
Shoot - I was banking on his answers being in the wrong order (?) oh well, keep trying
Well thats what I get for being a good Old man and putting some dirty cloths in tha wash I missed again
Timing is everything.   I just logged in at the time TJ posted  Wifey will be pleased
